reviewText: Sometimes it's best to stick with the original.
This was a hard item to find.  It was in very good shape but was very short in length.  I expected more.

I  was disappointed that it was so short.  I actually wanted the original work out, so this was my fault for ordering the wrong one.  But, I thought this was so short, and not worth the money.  I had had the original work out video with the bar, and it stopped playing ( I guess the tape broke), and I wanted to start exercising again.
